 high-temperature\nexpansions of the classical model, while they are limited by graph counting for\nthe $T=0$ quantum system. Details of the calculational methods are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Sep 2017 21:52:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-03"}
