aker flares. This\nwork demonstrates the potential to use statistical properties of X-ray flares\nto probe their trigger and emission mechanisms, as well as the radiation\npropagation around the black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2017 07:04:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Oct 2017 09:06:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-20"}
