rous mathematical proof. Experimental\nresults on two publicly available HSI data sets demonstrate that the proposed\nmethodology outperforms ELM and a number of state-of-the-art approaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2017 11:39:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 Oct 2017 12:25:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-15"}
